{"id": 1263, "genre": 1001, "title": "从学校毕业之后，你最为什么事情感到焦虑？", "description": "有人把二十多岁年轻人压力爆表的状态叫做“人生四分之一危机”，你有吗？（题图来自：Sophie Blackhall-Cain）", "record_count": 7374, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20161009162321VH8x9PKWtERizdXe.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2016-10-20T03:00:22Z", "options": [{"id": 125952, "content": "心比天高，命比纸薄", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 802797}, {"id": 126208, "content": "现在正在一间国企实习，现在被调岗到一个偏僻的产业园实习工作，一天工作12个小时，原定于六个月的实习期和签了六个月的试用期合同，但现在已过了四个月，到时候是走还是留，挺迷茫的。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 692819}, {"id": 134657, "content": "毕业出来为止没有做过像样的工作 想改变现状 却又有心无力", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 836717}, {"id": 352257, "content": "去学习", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1490462}, {"id": 125953, "content": "考研，还是同等学力考研！", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 766691}, {"id": 126209, "content": "即不安于现状，又没能力改变一切", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 803621}, {"id": 125954, "content": "还没有考到心仪的研究生院", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 743270}, {"id": 126210, "content": "想做自己喜欢的事，却不得不重复做讨厌的事赚钱。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 803627}, {"id": 126466, "content": "没工作", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 803805}, {"id": 128002, "content": "没钱、没车、没房、没工作、没女朋友！?", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 806723}, {"id": 126211, "content": "还没毕业，来看看，免得将来措手不及", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 799547}, {"id": 125956, "content": "赚钱", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 149389}, {"id": 126212, "content": "喜欢的人再也见不到", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 803640}, {"id": 126468, "content": "我最害怕。 人生已经过去四分之一。但是还是没有了解自己，也不知道自己到底想要什么。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 763298}, {"id": 127748, "content": "不满意现状，但是又毫无目标～", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 788109}, {"id": 125957, "content": "赚更多钱", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 149389}, {"id": 126213, "content": "想着怎么挣钱。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 480866}, {"id": 125958, "content": "还是工作吧...想努力考进编制....但是目前却没有安稳的环境...无法静下心来！", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 797587}, {"id": 126214, "content": "离自己的梦想越来越远\n和别人的差距越来越大\n渐渐感觉到有社会阶层", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 803648}, {"id": 134151, "content": "步入新环境，接触新工作，", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 834713}, {"id": 125959, "content": "房子，车子，票子，最关键是孩子", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 118590}, {"id": 126215, "content": "接下来该怎么做好每一步。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 803653}, {"id": 125960, "content": "房子，车子，票子，最关键是孩子", "image": "img/option/option/20161020173902ARHJnaoNjPvmiMzw", "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 118590}, {"id": 126216, "content": "生活波澜不惊一成不变\n对生活提不起任何兴趣\n每天混吃等死。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 803648}, {"id": 125961, "content": "前面两排都点了━ ~ ━", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 539204}, {"id": 126217, "content": "怕偏离理想和目标", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 778229}, {"id": 126985, "content": "怕以后连自己都养不起 ", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 807601}, {"id": 125962, "content": "怎么才能做到做爱做的事又能养活自己", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 802810}, {"id": 125963, "content": "本人大三。对未来无限迷茫，求高人指点迷津。", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 799888}, {"id": 126219, "content": "年轻有着一万种机会 却在一次次的懒惰中慌忙而过 毫无目的 磕磕碰碰的机会都没有", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 803668}, {"id": 125964, "content": "aaa", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 626549}, {"id": 128268, "content": "找工作，", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 704221}, {"id": 125965, "content": "人生的转折点 工作家庭都在这个年龄段就要稳定下来", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 771110}, {"id": 126477, "content": "工作啊，工资啊，北上广深打工仔什么时候有个家(还有就是女票出国后异地(T_T))", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 790098}, {"id": 125966, "content": "我以为的我以为并不是我以为的", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 713934}, {"id": 126223, "content": "事业没起色。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 684134}, {"id": 125968, "content": "有了一定的物质基础，但搞不清楚自己接下来生活工作方向", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 782691}, {"id": 125969, "content": "长辈催婚，并觉得\"还结婚的年纪就应该结婚\"", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 800987}, {"id": 126737, "content": "时间不自由", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 806081}, {"id": 134162, "content": "没钱啊", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 834202}, {"id": 125970, "content": "工作每天都是那些事，无聊又忙碌。没有周末没有假期，想换工作，家庭条件却不允许任性。不知道未来的路在哪里。迷茫又着急。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 737576}, {"id": 126226, "content": "想过更好的生活却没有那个能力。眼高于手也只能在底层拼命地攀爬", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 803683}, {"id": 125971, "content": "还有一年才毕业，好好把握现在", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 784643}, {"id": 126483, "content": "没钱没车没房没对象。人生有些迷茫…", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 805071}, {"id": 125972, "content": "再也不会安心理得的休假了，", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 802844}, {"id": 126228, "content": "没钱，想赚钱，还没有未来规划", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 753488}, {"id": 125973, "content": "天真的我终于看清了生活不只眼前的苟且，还有远方的巨坑", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 802738}, {"id": 126229, "content": "工资不高的稳定工作 总觉得生活在活死人墓 却找不到自己的目标 因此迷茫挫败", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 586732}, {"id": 125974, "content": "想回去上学", "image": null, "praise_count": 17, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 760783}, {"id": 126230, "content": "只想说曾梦想仗剑走天涯~_~;", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 797951}]}